football team is not a new idea.

352
00:24:48,240 --> 00:24:49,759
Dodge,

353
00:24:49,760 --> 00:24:52,559
we had some laughs a few years ago.

354
00:24:52,560 --> 00:24:55,560
-You had some laughs.
-(CHUCKLlNG) Yes.

