365
00:25:18,560 --> 00:25:20,239
DODGE: The President
gave you a medal for bravery.

366
00:25:20,240 --> 00:25:22,319
CARTER: l was just in
the right place at the right time.

367
00:25:22,320 --> 00:25:25,320
